- I don't know.

03:00.777 --> 03:02.745
Just get-- get him down.
Watch out, watch out!

03:02.746 --> 03:05.315
- He swallowed a lot of water.
- Sit him up!

03:05.316 --> 03:07.149
- Sit him up.
- Sit him up.

03:07.150 --> 03:08.851
- Go!
- Get him on his back.

03:08.852 --> 03:10.520
I'll try C.P.R.

03:12.356 --> 03:14.290
Stop!

03:14.291 --> 03:16.559
Are you all right?
You all right?

03:16.560 --> 03:18.661
What happened there?

03:19.996 --> 03:21.764
I fell in the water.

03:21.765 --> 03:23.932
No, he didn't!
I saw him.

03:23.933 --> 03:25.735
- He jumped.
- <i>Breathe, breathe.</i>

03:25.736 --> 03:27.270
What are you talking about?
I fell in the water.

03:27.271 --> 03:29.272
- <i>He just jumped in.</i>
- Come on, I gotta go!

03:29.273 --> 03:30.435
Just take it easy, man.
Where you going?

03:30.436 --> 03:30.973
Where you going?

03:30.974 --> 03:33.116
You gotta wait
for the cops, man.

03:33.117 --> 03:33.242
Hey!

03:33.243 --> 03:35.744
Hey, buddy, you even gonna thank
the guy who just saved your life?

03:35.745 --> 03:35.977
Huh?

03:35.978 --> 03:38.581
This guy right here--
he just saved your life.

03:39.983 --> 03:41.917
Oh.
Thank you.

03:42.986 --> 03:44.587
<i>Jesus.</i>

03:44.588 --> 03:46.722
<i>Hey, ain't that the guy</i>
<i>that works over at the, uh,</i>

03:46.723 --> 03:48.891
<i>the dry-cleaner</i>
<i>on Neptune Avenue?</i>

03:48.892 --> 03:52.294
<i>Maybe. But he doesn't look</i>
<i>too dry to me now.</i>

03:52.295 --> 03:54.429
<i>Douchebag.</i>

03:54.430 --> 03:56.399
<i>From New York 1 News,</i>

03:56.400 --> 03:58.968
<i>This is</i>
<i>"New York Tonight."</i>

03:58.969 --> 04:01.621
Hello?

04:01.622 --> 04:05.808
<i>I was beginning to think</i>
<i>you weren't going to make it.</i>

04:05.809 --> 04:08.961
<i>We're having guests</i>
<i>for dinner tonight.</i>

04:11.931 --> 04:14.266
What-- what happened?

04:14.267 --> 04:15.718
Huh?

04:15.719 --> 04:17.553
You're all wet.

04:17.553 --> 04:19.572
I fell
into the bay.

04:19.572 --> 04:21.807
It's cold-- Mom, come
on, stop. I'm fine.

04:21.808 --> 04:23.876
- You fell into the bay?
- It's not gonna happen again.

04:23.877 --> 04:26.011
- <i>Don't worry.</i>
- Leonard.

04:26.012 --> 04:28.364
It was an accident.
Can I change, please?

04:28.365 --> 04:29.732
Reuben!

04:29.733 --> 04:32.368
Mom, I'm fine!
I'm fine.

04:33.854 --> 04:35.738
What is the matter?

04:35.739 --> 04:38.374
I think he
tried again.

04:38.375 --> 04:40.425
He said he fell
in the bay.

04:45.382 --> 04:46.882
Leonard?

04:46.883 --> 04:50.686
<i>I think he forgot</i>
<i>his medication this morning.</i>

04:50.687 --> 04:52.738
<i>Leonard?</i>

04:52.739 --> 04:56.241
<i>Listen-- the man who wants</i>
<i>to buy our business</i>

04:56.242 --> 04:58.394
<i>is coming over tonight</i>
<i>with his family.</i>

04:58.395 --> 04:59.762
<i>Let's cancel that.</i>

04:59.763 --> 05:01.246
<i>No, they're almost here.</i>

05:01.247 --> 05:04.516
<i>Look, if he still has</i>
<i>this bipolar problem,</i>

05:04.517 --> 05:06.569
<i>he just has to</i>
<i>take his pills.</i>

05:06.570 --> 05:10.222
<i>It would be nice if</i>
<i>you joined us, okay?</i>

05:10.223 --> 05:12.041
<i>'Cause we want you</i>
<i>to join us.</i>

05:12.042 --> 05:13.842
Okay.

05:26.490 --> 05:29.091
Stupid stupid.

05:31.594 --> 05:33.428
Hi, how are you?
Oh, enjoy.

05:33.429 --> 05:34.847
Thank you!

05:34.848 --> 05:36.949
- Hi.
- Hello.

05:36.950 --> 05:39.485
I hope we're not late.
The directions were perfect.

05:39.486 --> 05:41.387
- It smells good.
- How you feeling?

05:41.388 --> 05:42.671
Good,
thank you.

05:42.672 --> 05:45.124
Good. You remember
my wife Carol.

05:45.125 --> 05:46.792
Hi, nice to
see you again.

05:46.793 --> 05:49.545
- <i>Thank you so much.</i>
- <i>And these are my kids--</i>

05:49.546 --> 05:51.597
<i>--David, my son.</i>

05:51.598 --> 05:53.882
<i>David.</i>
<i>My beautiful daughter Sandra.</i>

05:53.883 --> 05:57.119
<i>Oh thanks, Dad.</i>
<i>Pleased to meet you.</i>

05:57.120 --> 05:58.654
I have to go
to the bathroom.

05:58.655 --> 06:00.789
Down at the end
of the hallway.

06:00.790 --> 06:02.591
Hey hey, David,
what you got?

06:02.592 --> 06:05.661
Ohh!

06:05.662 --> 06:07.362
David,
say thank you.

06:07.363 --> 06:09.665
All right. Come inside.
Let me take your coats.

06:09.666 --> 06:11.667
Yeah, take
the coats.

06:11.668 --> 06:13.920
- This is a beautiful place.
- Yeah, you like it?

06:13.921 --> 06:16.055
It's so nostalgic--
it's like the place I grew up in.

06:16.056 --> 06:17.506
<i>Eat what you'd like. Okay.</i>

06:17.507 --> 06:20.126
- They're not baked.
- They taste like baked.

06:20.127 --> 06:21.644
Okay.

06:21.645 --> 06:25.097
My wife-- my princess--
is in the kitchen getting dinner ready.

06:25.098 --> 06:27.866
She'll be right out.
Anyway, help yourself.

06:27.867 --> 06:30.236
It's homemade hummus.
I did it.

06:30.237 --> 06:32.271
- <i>Oh!</i>
- Yeah.

06:32.272 --> 06:33.939
<i>Mmm, terrific! Terrific!</i>

06:33.940 --> 06:37.325
- <i>Ooh!</i>
- This is my son Leonard.

06:37.326 --> 06:39.194
- How you doing?
- Leonard? Michael Cohen.

06:39.195 --> 06:40.412
- How do you do?
- Nice to meet you.

06:40.413 --> 06:41.864
My wife Carol,
my daughter Sandra.

06:41.865 --> 06:44.466
- Hi, how you doing?
- Hi.

06:44.467 --> 06:46.903
- Nice to meet you.
- Nice to meet you.

06:48.955 --> 06:50.156
<i>...Not from the Catskills.</i>

06:50.157 --> 06:51.774
<i>The Catskills that we</i>
<i>were talking about</i>

06:51.775 --> 06:53.776
<i>Is like</i>
<i>the slums of the Catskills.</i>

06:53.777 --> 06:57.379
- Which part? Which part?
- South Fallsburg, Loch Sheldrake.

06:57.380 --> 07:00.665
- Which is more west?
- Kiamesha. Kiamesha.

07:00.666 --> 07:02.334
<i>Is it more west than--</i>
- <i>We met at the Catskills.</i>

07:02.335 --> 07:04.520
<i>Just in time for the flies.</i>

07:04.521 --> 07:06.839
<i>You were very--</i>
- <i>And you were the prettiest one.</i>

07:06.840 --> 07:08.991
<i>I paid him to say that.</i>

07:08.992 --> 07:11.093
<i>35 years ago in</i>
<i>the Catskills.</i>

07:11.094 --> 07:12.211
<i>Please don't make me older.</i>

07:12.212 --> 07:15.247
- Hey, you like magic?
- Yeah.

07:15.248 --> 07:18.100
You ever heard of
the melting spoon?

07:18.101 --> 07:19.619
No.

07:19.620 --> 07:21.620
It's really cool.

07:21.621 --> 07:24.323
<i>Now they put so many</i>
<i>things in your path.</i>

07:24.324 --> 07:27.392
<i>I mean, all the inspections</i>
<i>and all of the licensing</i>

07:27.393 --> 07:30.462
<i>and all the-- the different</i>
<i>technology-- the machines.</i>

07:30.463 --> 07:32.197
<i>It's amazing you can</i>
<i>run a business.</i>

07:32.198 --> 07:34.333
You know, my son's been
working with me a little

07:34.334 --> 07:36.185
since he's been back.

07:36.186 --> 07:38.754
<i>You know?</i>
<i>I don't know how much he likes it, but...</i>

07:42.976 --> 07:44.893
<i>What about it, Lenny?</i>
<i>Do you like it?</i>

07:44.894 --> 07:46.595
<i>Do you like</i>
<i>the dry-cleaning business?</i>

07:46.596 --> 07:49.998
It's all right, you know?
It's good to help out the family.

07:49.999 --> 07:52.417
<i>He's a good photographer--</i>
<i>I'll tell you that.</i>

07:52.418 --> 07:54.286
<i>Really?</i>
- Yes. Yes yes.

07:54.287 --> 07:56.355
Yeah, I gave him
an old camera

07:56.356 --> 07:59.257
and now all he does--
he takes pictures all over the place.

07:59.258 --> 08:00.609
<i>Really?</i>

08:00.610 --> 08:02.177
<i>Beautiful black-and-white photos.</i>

08:02.178 --> 08:03.528
<i>Black and white.</i>
- Thanks, Mom.

08:03.529 --> 08:05.481
Yes, they are
beautiful photos.

08:05.482 --> 08:07.633
<i>Carol?</i>
- <i>Yes?</i>

08:07.634 --> 08:09.985
- Do you know what I'm thinking right--
- I know what you're thinking.

08:09.986 --> 08:11.637
<i>Listen, I have a little</i>
<i>proposition.</i>

08:11.638 --> 08:14.240
- Mmm, here we go.
- <i>No no.</i>

08:14.241 --> 08:16.592
We have-- we have
a bar mitzvah.

08:16.593 --> 08:18.827
David's bar mitzvah
is coming up next week.

08:18.828 --> 08:20.863
Oh, and of course
you're all invited.

08:20.864 --> 08:22.297
- You're invited.
- Oh, thank you.

08:22.298 --> 08:24.466
Oh, yeah.
- But we have a photographer,

08:24.467 --> 08:27.269
and he's taking the color shots and
he's taking the slides and the set-ups,

08:27.270 --> 08:29.821
but my wife,
the artistic one,

08:29.822 --> 08:31.207
she wants
the black and white.

08:31.208 --> 08:33.174
Yes, we do.
- Lenny?

08:33.176 --> 08:35.894
<i>Do you think you'd be interested
in doing something like that?</i>

08:35.895 --> 08:37.629
Oh, I don't know
about that.

08:37.630 --> 08:39.482
- I mean, I--
- <i>Why not?</i>

08:39.482 --> 08:41.283
I don't-- I don't really
do impromptu things.

08:41.284 --> 08:44.302
- I mean--
- Oh, try. You'll see what happens.

08:44.303 --> 08:46.471
<i>I'd love to see his stuff--</i>

08:46.472 --> 08:49.108
just check it out a little bit.
Do you think I could?

08:49.109 --> 08:50.909
Okay.

08:50.910 --> 08:52.928
I'll show you some.

08:52.929 --> 08:55.664
Leonard, why don't you show
Sandra your pictures?

08:55.665 --> 08:58.134
I don't know if--
you want to see that now?

08:58.135 --> 08:59.751
Yeah, I'd love
to see them.

08:59.752 --> 09:02.087
'Kay.
Come on.

09:02.088 --> 09:05.140
<i>I tell him all the time</i>
<i>but he gets angry at me.</i>

09:06.510 --> 09:08.727
- Report back.
- I'll call you for dessert.

09:08.728 --> 09:10.078
Eh?

09:12.799 --> 09:15.134
I wasn't expecting
visitors.

09:17.570 --> 09:19.504
Yeah, you've got
a lot of stuff in here.

09:19.505 --> 09:21.006
Yeah.

09:21.007 --> 09:23.375
I wasn't planning on being
home for so long, so...

09:23.376 --> 09:25.978
I gotta organize this place.
I don't know what the fuck.

09:25.979 --> 09:28.013
Oh, when--
when did you get back?

09:28.014 --> 09:30.015
Uh, about
four months ago.

09:30.016 --> 09:31.250
Mmm.

09:31.251 --> 09:33.702
What are we doing?
Oh, yeah-- pictures.

09:33.703 --> 09:35.604
You can sit down
if you want.

09:35.605 --> 09:37.105
Okay.

09:41.144 --> 09:43.912
- Let's see.
- You have a lot of DVDs.

09:43.913 --> 09:46.014
Yeah.
You like movies?

09:46.015 --> 09:47.449
Yeah, I love
movies.

09:47.450 --> 09:49.451
Yeah? Like what?
What do you like?

09:49.452 --> 09:52.504
Well, my favorite
movie is probably...

09:52.505 --> 09:54.056
"The Sound of Music."

09:54.057 --> 09:57.158
<i>Not because of</i>
<i>the film, really,</i>

09:57.159 --> 09:59.444
but because, you know,
whenever it's on,

09:59.445 --> 10:01.930
my family always watches it.
It's that kind of thing.

10:01.931 --> 10:04.466
No, that's a good movie.
It's underrated.

10:04.467 --> 10:06.535
Yeah.

10:06.536 --> 10:08.020
Can I look at these?

10:08.021 --> 10:10.022
Yeah, those are--
that's a good pile.

10:10.023 --> 10:12.757
<i>This is</i>
<i>the garbage pile.</i>

10:14.978 --> 10:17.262
Oh, these are nice.

10:17.263 --> 10:18.864
<i>Oh, thanks.</i>

10:18.865 --> 10:20.599
<i>Yeah, this one I like.</i>
<i>Look at it.</i>

10:20.600 --> 10:22.634
This one's nice too.

10:22.635 --> 10:26.188
But you don't have any
people in them really.

10:26.189 --> 10:28.273
Yeah, well,
you know.

10:28.274 --> 10:30.876
People look at 'em-- they
don't have to be in 'em too.

10:30.877 --> 10:32.477
I like this one.

10:32.478 --> 10:35.114
<i>Thanks.</i>
<i>Gotta be in the moment.</i>

10:36.832 --> 10:39.534
So what--
what do you do?

10:39.535 --> 10:43.955
I work at Pfizer in
the city-- it's a drug company.

10:43.956 --> 10:46.425
Yeah, I know it well.

10:46.426 --> 10:49.628
I have some ones with
some people in it.

10:49.629 --> 10:51.397
I was just
going through these--

10:51.398 --> 10:55.383
who's-- who's that
in this photo here?

10:57.237 --> 11:01.473
Oh, that was-- I don't even
know what that's doing there.

11:01.474 --> 11:04.125
That's so weird.
That was my fiancée.

11:04.126 --> 11:06.829
- Your fiancée?
- <i>Yeah.</i>

11:06.830 --> 11:08.714
You were engaged.

11:08.715 --> 11:11.801
Yeah,
a couple years ago.

11:13.052 --> 11:15.688
She's gone, though.
She moved away.

11:17.290 --> 11:18.740
What happened?

11:18.741 --> 11:21.560
You know, um--

11:21.561 --> 11:24.246
We got these genetic tests
and we were both positive

11:24.247 --> 11:26.615
- for Tay-Sachs disease.
- Oh.

11:26.616 --> 11:30.251
It means if we ever had kids, they'd
be, like, dead after a year, so...

11:30.252 --> 11:31.737
<i>Yeah.</i>

11:31.738 --> 11:33.606
She didn't want to adopt

11:33.607 --> 11:36.441
and, well,
that was that.

11:36.442 --> 11:39.244
I'm so sorry.

11:39.245 --> 11:42.581
Mmm, probably for
the best.

11:42.582 --> 11:44.549
<i>Leonard? Sandra?</i>

11:44.550 --> 11:46.018
<i>Dessert's on the table.</i>

11:46.019 --> 11:48.370
Okay!

11:48.371 --> 11:51.090
You know, um...

11:51.091 --> 11:54.043
our parents
wanted us to meet.

11:56.796 --> 12:00.332
<i>Well, no, I have to</i>
<i>tell you the truth.</i>

12:00.333 --> 12:03.285
Actually, I wanted
to meet you.

12:06.272 --> 12:08.590
Yeah?

12:08.591 --> 12:10.242
Yeah.

12:10.243 --> 12:12.528
I saw you at
your parents' store

12:12.529 --> 12:14.462
and I just...

12:14.463 --> 12:18.133
You were asking
your mother to dance with you.

12:18.134 --> 12:20.285
<i>It was</i>
<i>very cute.</i>

12:21.871 --> 12:24.223
Sounds like something
I would do.

12:24.224 --> 12:27.125
<i>You two, dessert's on the table.</i>

12:27.126 --> 12:29.310
Yeah, we heard you
the first time!

12:31.748 --> 12:33.582
Sorry.

12:33.583 --> 12:35.484
She's really serious
about her desserts.

12:37.203 --> 12:39.871
We should probably go.
She's...

12:39.872 --> 12:42.374
gonna have an aneurysm.

12:42.375 --> 12:44.376
- We'll hang out after.
- Okay.

12:44.377 --> 12:47.146
Um, yeah. Okay.
I'm just gonna put this away.

13:22.349 --> 13:24.350
<i>Leonard?</i>

13:24.351 --> 13:26.718
Stop horsing around.

13:29.839 --> 13:32.140
Three deliveries--
one right near here

13:32.141 --> 13:34.676
and the other two
are in Sheepshead Bay.

13:34.677 --> 13:35.744
Okay.

13:35.745 --> 13:37.780
And don't lose
the clothes again.

13:37.781 --> 13:41.783
- You're gonna put us out of business.
- God willing.

14:20.239 --> 14:23.742
<i>We'll only be here</i>
<i>for a few months.</i>

14:23.743 --> 14:25.611
- <i>Hey, don't walk away.</i>
- <i>Don't fucking touch me.</i>

14:25.612 --> 14:27.613
- <i>Hey hey, where are you going?</i>
- <i>Get your fucking hands off me.</i>

14:27.614 --> 14:29.998
<i>Don't walk away from me!</i>
<i>Michelle!</i>

14:31.551 --> 14:34.536
<i>Get the fuck</i>
<i>back up here!</i>

14:34.537 --> 14:37.355
<i>Do not</i>
<i>disrespect me!</i>

14:38.974 --> 14:41.092
- Hi.
- Hi.

14:41.093 --> 14:42.711
<i>You're such</i>
<i>a spoiled brat!</i>

14:42.712 --> 14:44.496
Sorry.

14:44.497 --> 14:47.599
- For what?
- <i>You still think you're living up in great neck?</i>

14:47.600 --> 14:51.920
It's my father.
He's-- he's a little crazy.

14:51.921 --> 14:53.572
You okay?

14:53.573 --> 14:55.407
<i>Yeah.</i>

14:55.408 --> 14:57.876
<i>Hey, I can hear you talking.</i>
<i>Who are you talking to down there?</i>

14:57.877 --> 14:59.895
Do--
you live here, right?

14:59.896 --> 15:02.514
Yeah. Well, my parents do.
I'm staying with them.

15:02.515 --> 15:03.982
Oh, right.

15:03.983 --> 15:06.651
<i>Michelle, come back here.</i>
<i>Don't leave like this.</i>

15:06.652 --> 15:08.420
You want to
come in for a bit?

15:08.421 --> 15:11.489
Yeah, maybe just--
that'd be great.

15:11.490 --> 15:13.591
Just until he
calms down, maybe.

15:13.592 --> 15:15.693
I don't want, like,
everybody to call the cops.

15:15.694 --> 15:17.428
Yeah, that'd suck.

15:17.429 --> 15:18.730
I'm Leonard.

15:18.731 --> 15:19.831
- Michelle.
- Michelle.

15:19.832 --> 15:22.383
Yeah, you can
hear him screaming.

15:22.384 --> 15:25.770
<i>Come on up here!</i>
<i>Don't make me shout.</i>

15:25.771 --> 15:27.839
Hey, do you think
you want anything?

15:27.840 --> 15:30.342
- No.
- <i>Hello?</i>

15:30.343 --> 15:31.876
Hi.

15:31.877 --> 15:35.380
- Oh, Mom, this is Michelle--
- I'm-- I'm your neighbor.

15:35.381 --> 15:37.232
<i>Hello, neighbor.</i>

15:37.233 --> 15:39.668
<i>Leonard,</i>
<i>your dad just came home.</i>

15:39.669 --> 15:41.986
We're going to have
Chinese food.

15:41.987 --> 15:43.238
<i>Okay.</i>

15:43.239 --> 15:44.973
That's nice.

15:50.163 --> 15:52.464
Oh, what are
those things?

15:52.465 --> 15:53.798
- What, that?
- Yeah.

15:53.799 --> 15:55.467
Oh, that's a dreidel.

16:02.175 --> 16:04.376
Ha.
What?

16:04.377 --> 16:06.728
It smells
like mothballs.

16:06.729 --> 16:08.263
It does?

16:08.264 --> 16:10.966
No, it's a good thing.
It reminds me of my grandma's house.

16:10.967 --> 16:13.101
