didn't call me back.

51:12.299 --> 51:13.716
I--

51:13.717 --> 51:16.018
We don't have
to go out.

51:16.019 --> 51:19.188
I mean,

51:19.189 --> 51:23.510
There are a lot of
guys who just--

51:23.511 --> 51:26.696
That want to
go out with me.

51:47.435 --> 51:49.669
Oh my--
oh my God.

51:57.611 --> 51:59.645
I do like you.

52:11.225 --> 52:12.976
Well, it feels
a little strange

52:12.977 --> 52:15.327
with my mother
staring right there.

53:16.923 --> 53:18.358
Mmm.

53:19.793 --> 53:22.311
I should go

53:22.312 --> 53:26.282
before your parents come home
and see us like this.

53:26.283 --> 53:28.201
Are you kidding?
They'd be happy.

53:28.202 --> 53:30.236
Probably picking out
baby names.

53:32.139 --> 53:33.372
God.

53:41.832 --> 53:43.933
So I heard you're going to
take the pictures

53:43.934 --> 53:46.302
at my brother's
bar mitzvah next month.

53:46.303 --> 53:47.637
<i>Yeah.</i>

53:47.638 --> 53:49.956
I'm taking the black
and whites-- the art shots.

53:49.957 --> 53:52.324
<i>That's cool.</i>

53:52.325 --> 53:54.977
My friend's having
a party on Thursday night.

53:54.978 --> 53:56.429
You wanna come?

53:56.430 --> 53:58.648
I'll try to see
if I'm free.

53:58.649 --> 54:00.166
Okay.

54:03.170 --> 54:04.603
Will you call me?

54:04.604 --> 54:05.839
Yeah.

54:07.808 --> 54:09.575
<i>I'll see myself out.</i>

54:09.576 --> 54:10.877
<i>Okay.</i>

54:11.946 --> 54:14.613
- Bye.
- <i>Bye.</i>

54:47.998 --> 54:51.000
- Hey.
- <i>Leonard, could you meet me up on the roof?</i>

54:51.001 --> 54:52.285
What time is it?

54:52.286 --> 54:54.037
<i>It's early.</i>
<i>It's like 6:30.</i>

54:54.038 --> 54:55.437
<i>Could you come up?</i>

54:55.438 --> 54:58.440
Oh, yeah.
Yeah, I'll come up now.

54:58.441 --> 55:00.143
- <i>Thanks.</i>
- Right.

55:12.055 --> 55:14.307
- Hey.
- Hi.

55:14.308 --> 55:15.841
It's fucking cold.

55:15.842 --> 55:19.245
I know. I'm sorry,
but he's downstairs.

55:19.246 --> 55:21.180
So what did
you think?

55:29.807 --> 55:32.775
Leonard, what did you think of Ronald?
Tell me.

55:36.213 --> 55:38.564
I don't know.

55:38.565 --> 55:41.434
What-- what do you
want me to say?

55:45.972 --> 55:48.540
Do you think he's going
to be with me for good?

55:52.596 --> 55:55.064
Seriously.

55:55.065 --> 55:56.766
I don't think so.

55:58.585 --> 56:00.236
Sorry.

56:09.429 --> 56:12.932
He's got this fucking business
trip he wants me to go on.

56:12.933 --> 56:14.667
I don't know what to do.

56:15.903 --> 56:19.138
Michelle, come on!
What are you doing?

56:20.573 --> 56:22.708
Come on, seriously.
He's the kind of guy

56:22.709 --> 56:25.244
who's got this
whole life,

56:25.245 --> 56:27.129
His family
and shit.

56:27.130 --> 56:29.765
You think he's gonna
leave all that?

56:32.202 --> 56:34.053
I know
I would.

56:36.891 --> 56:39.375
I'd definitely leave
everything for you.

56:44.715 --> 56:47.016
Leonard, you're very sweet,
but I--

56:47.017 --> 56:50.119
I think if you knew me better,
you wouldn't feel that way.

56:51.939 --> 56:54.139
I don't care.

56:54.140 --> 56:56.292
Leonard, listen to me.

56:56.293 --> 56:58.210
You're like a brother
to me now.

56:58.211 --> 56:58.333
Oh!

56:58.334 --> 57:00.647
I know we've only known each
other for a couple of weeks.

57:00.648 --> 57:03.249
But I-- I feel like I
could tell you anything.

57:03.250 --> 57:05.818
You know? I need you
to be my friend.

57:05.819 --> 57:08.287
You know, why don't you
tell Ronald, okay?

57:08.288 --> 57:10.289
Tell Ronald.
Go away on your trip--

57:10.290 --> 57:12.191
- <i>Tell Ronald?</i>
- I don't care.

57:12.192 --> 57:14.593
Have a great time.

57:14.594 --> 57:16.779
Leonard, where
are you going?

57:16.780 --> 57:18.781
I don't think we should
see each other anymore.

57:18.782 --> 57:20.783
Oh, Leonard,
don't say that.

57:22.552 --> 57:24.153
Leonard!

57:58.304 --> 58:00.305
Hey, Sandra,
it's Leonard.

58:00.306 --> 58:02.875
Uh, I know it's really early.
You're probably sleeping,

58:02.876 --> 58:05.711
but I was just checking
my schedule and I'm free.

58:05.712 --> 58:09.381
And, yeah-- see about maybe
going out with you to this party.

58:09.382 --> 58:12.085
So why don't you call me
when you get this?

58:12.086 --> 58:15.121
All right.
Hey, Happy Thanksgiving.

58:15.122 --> 58:16.889
Bye.

59:06.840 --> 59:09.759
<i>David, give us a turn.</i>
<i>Give us a turn.</i>

59:09.760 --> 59:12.294
<i>How does he look?</i>

59:12.295 --> 59:14.180
<i>And as our last event</i>
<i>of the day,</i>

59:14.181 --> 59:16.765
<i>I'd like to invite mom,</i>
<i>dad and sister Sandra</i>

59:16.766 --> 59:19.635
<i>to come up and give you support
for your candle-lighting.</i>

59:24.674 --> 59:26.175
<i>We're gonna share the love.</i>

59:26.176 --> 59:27.676
<i>Bring everybody</i>
<i>real close.</i>

59:27.677 --> 59:29.445
<i>Come on in, come around.</i>

59:29.446 --> 59:31.147
<i>Not so close.</i>

59:34.151 --> 59:35.985
<i>It's been such a great</i>
<i>afternoon, everybody.</i>

59:35.986 --> 59:37.420
<i>What a way to</i>
<i>wrap things up.</i>

59:40.790 --> 59:44.227
Our host, dad Michael,
would like to say a few words.

59:44.228 --> 59:46.662
If you could give him a
tremendous round of applause...

59:49.366 --> 59:51.467
Thank you.

59:51.468 --> 59:53.569
<i>Thank you, thank you.</i>

59:55.606 --> 59:58.774
<i>I just want to say that--</i>
<i>how proud I am</i>

59:58.775 --> 01:00:02.645
That everybody took the time
to come to David's bar mitzvah.

01:00:02.646 --> 01:00:05.814
And on behalf of
your sister Sandra

01:00:05.815 --> 01:00:07.483
and your mother Carol,

01:00:07.484 --> 01:00:10.319
I want to tell you
how proud we are of you.

01:00:10.320 --> 01:00:14.323
<i>I just have one question:</i>
<i>With all your gifts,</i>

01:00:14.324 --> 01:00:16.492
Can you make me
a $200 Loan?

01:00:18.328 --> 01:00:20.229
Okay, we're going to
light the last can--

01:00:20.230 --> 01:00:21.830
Leonard, come on
up with us.

01:00:21.831 --> 01:00:24.667
<i>My daughter's boyfriend,
everybody-- come on.</i>

01:00:24.668 --> 01:00:27.136
We're going to light
a candle for David.

01:00:38.182 --> 01:00:40.183
<i>All right, David, at this time</i>

01:00:40.184 --> 01:00:41.917
<i>I'd like you to</i>
<i>close your eyes</i>

01:00:41.918 --> 01:00:43.986
<i>and make a big wish.</i>

01:00:49.660 --> 01:00:51.227
He's very popular.

01:00:51.228 --> 01:00:54.196
I thought it was on silent.
Excuse me. I'm sorry.

01:00:54.197 --> 01:00:56.999
Help me count, everybody.
Here we go-- one two...

01:00:57.000 --> 01:00:59.201
- Three--
- <i>blow out those candles!</i>

01:01:01.371 --> 01:01:03.739
Ah, <i>mazel tov!</i>

01:01:07.978 --> 01:01:09.679
<i>Last dance, everybody.</i>

01:01:09.680 --> 01:01:13.015
<i>Everybody up for the last dance!</i>
<i>Come on.</i>

01:01:27.097 --> 01:01:29.932
<i>Good night, Leonard.</i>
- Bye.

01:01:36.906 --> 01:01:38.574
<i>Leonard?</i>

01:01:38.575 --> 01:01:41.277
I saw you called me.
What do you want?

01:01:41.278 --> 01:01:42.612
<i>I'm sorry.</i>

01:01:42.613 --> 01:01:44.463
<i>I know you don't want</i>
<i>to talk to me,</i>

01:01:44.464 --> 01:01:46.766
<i>But I don't-- I don't</i>
<i>know what else to do.</i>

01:01:46.767 --> 01:01:50.136
<i>Um, I'm not</i>
<i>feeling well.</i>

01:01:50.137 --> 01:01:51.653
What's wrong?

01:01:51.654 --> 01:01:54.173
<i>I was supposed to go</i>
<i>to the doctor today.</i>

01:01:54.174 --> 01:01:56.241
<i>I'm-- I'm at home</i>
<i>right now.</i>

01:01:56.242 --> 01:01:59.311
<i>Ron was supposed to take me,
but I don't know where he is.</i>

01:01:59.312 --> 01:02:03.132
<i>I started bleeding really</i>
<i>bad a few hours ago.</i>

01:02:03.133 --> 01:02:04.666
You're bleeding?

01:02:04.667 --> 01:02:06.485
<i>I may need to go to</i>
<i>the hospital,</i>

01:02:06.486 --> 01:02:08.654
<i>but I'm afraid</i>
<i>to go by myself.</i>

01:02:08.655 --> 01:02:10.822
<i>Can you come</i>
<i>with me, please?</i>

01:02:10.823 --> 01:02:12.707
Yeah, I'll come.

01:02:12.708 --> 01:02:14.826
<i>Thank you so much,</i>
<i>Leonard.</i>

01:02:31.227 --> 01:02:33.862
<i>Leonard?</i>

01:02:33.863 --> 01:02:37.349
<i>Hey.</i> What are you
<i>doing down here?</i>

01:02:37.350 --> 01:02:40.119
What happened?

01:02:45.025 --> 01:02:47.192
I don't feel
very well.

01:02:49.045 --> 01:02:51.730
I'm scared something's
gonna happen.

01:02:52.982 --> 01:02:55.684
Wait here. I'll try
and get us a cab.

01:03:16.890 --> 01:03:19.191
<i>Mr. Kraditor?</i>

01:03:19.192 --> 01:03:20.592
<i>Come.</i>

01:03:32.272 --> 01:03:33.939
Is she awake?

01:03:33.940 --> 01:03:35.941
Yeah.

01:03:35.942 --> 01:03:38.444
<i>But she's still</i>
<i>sedated.</i>

01:03:38.445 --> 01:03:41.347
Mmm, Leonard.

01:03:42.615 --> 01:03:44.183
How you feelin'?

01:03:44.184 --> 01:03:47.987
Is there another blanket?
I'm so cold.

01:03:47.988 --> 01:03:51.290
Yeah, I can feel that.

01:03:51.291 --> 01:03:54.026
Hey, she feels really cold.
Is that normal?

01:03:54.027 --> 01:03:56.361
Yeah, that's typical
from the anesthesia.

01:03:56.362 --> 01:04:01.366
<i>She should be fine. She just needs
to see a doctor in a couple of weeks.</i>

01:04:01.367 --> 01:04:03.435
What'd they do
to her?

01:04:03.436 --> 01:04:05.670
The doctor had to
perform a D. and C.

01:04:05.671 --> 01:04:07.672
She miscarried.

01:04:07.673 --> 01:04:10.943
She wasn't aware she was
pregnant until she came in today.

01:04:18.818 --> 01:04:22.621
They said you're okay
and that's what's important.

01:04:26.593 --> 01:04:28.394
I know.

01:04:46.146 --> 01:04:48.914
Rex, hi.

01:04:48.915 --> 01:04:50.549
Oh, come in.

01:04:50.550 --> 01:04:52.852
This is my dog, Rex.

01:04:52.853 --> 01:04:54.386
Oh hi, Rex.

01:04:54.387 --> 01:04:57.022
Oh.

01:04:57.023 --> 01:04:59.591
Leonard, I gotta
go lie down.

01:04:59.592 --> 01:05:01.193
Yeah, you should.

01:05:01.194 --> 01:05:03.028
Okay, I'll bring you
the pillows.

01:05:03.029 --> 01:05:04.563
Thank you.

01:05:10.837 --> 01:05:13.805
I brought you
some water.

01:05:16.476 --> 01:05:18.110
Thank you, Leonard.

01:05:18.111 --> 01:05:19.778
Feelin' better?

01:05:19.779 --> 01:05:22.047
Good.

01:05:22.048 --> 01:05:25.383
I had these crazy
nightmares while I was out.

01:05:25.384 --> 01:05:27.385
Yeah?

01:05:27.386 --> 01:05:29.154
Don't worry.

01:05:29.155 --> 01:05:30.856
I am here
to protect you.

01:05:30.857 --> 01:05:32.657
Ow.

01:05:32.658 --> 01:05:34.760
- Don't make me laugh.
- All right.

01:05:34.761 --> 01:05:36.728
Oh, you'll protect me?

01:05:36.729 --> 01:05:38.897
Yeah. I have
a black belt, you know?

01:05:38.898 --> 01:05:39.798
Nightmares--

01:05:39.799 --> 01:05:41.400
It's fine. Shh.

01:05:41.401 --> 01:05:43.669
Oh, fuck.

01:05:43.670 --> 01:05:46.938
<i>Honey?</i>
- <i>If he sees you, he'll go crazy.</i>

01:05:46.939 --> 01:05:50.809
<i>Hey, what are you
doing, little guy?</i>

01:05:50.810 --> 01:05:53.144
<i>Sweetheart?</i>

01:05:53.145 --> 01:05:54.947
Hey.

01:05:54.948 --> 01:05:57.582
Oh hey, sweetheart.

01:05:59.519 --> 01:06:01.353
You didn't call me.

01:06:01.354 --> 01:06:03.422
I'm sorry.
I couldn't.

01:06:03.423 --> 01:06:06.224
My wife was with me all day.
I'm sorry, baby.

01:06:06.225 --> 01:06:09.228
I got here as quick
as I could.

01:06:09.229 --> 01:06:12.064
Today of all days?

01:06:12.065 --> 01:06:15.767
- <i>It's my wife.</i>
- Oh, fuck you.

01:06:15.768 --> 01:06:18.570
<i>She was just with me</i>
<i>all day.</i>

01:06:18.571 --> 01:06:20.372
Baby, I'm sorry.

01:06:20.373 --> 01:06:22.407
I really am sorry.

01:06:22.408 --> 01:06:25.677
<i>I thought about you all day.</i>
<i>It was killing me,</i>

01:06:25.678 --> 01:06:28.013
<i>thinking about you</i>
<i>at the hospital like that.</i>

01:06:29.548 --> 01:06:32.117
<i>What happened?</i>
<i>What did the doctor say?</i>

01:06:32.118 --> 01:06:33.752
<i>What's wrong?</i>

01:06:33.753 --> 01:06:37.789
Um, I don't feel very well.
I want to be by myself.

01:06:39.258 --> 01:06:41.159
You're not gonna let me
stay with you,

01:06:41.160 --> 01:06:42.928
- even just for a few minutes?
- No.

01:06:42.929 --> 01:06:46.131
I don't want you to stay
with me for a few minutes.

01:06:46.132 --> 01:06:49.802
Honey, I have to go
to London tomorrow night.

01:06:49.803 --> 01:06:52.771
And then I'm not going to
see you for two weeks.

01:06:57.210 --> 01:06:59.678
I'm sorry.

01:06:59.679 --> 01:07:01.280
I'm sorry.

01:07:04.984 --> 01:07:07.152
I tried to get here
as soon as I could.

01:07:07.153 --> 01:07:09.221
Yeah.

01:07:09.222 --> 01:07:12.157
Come on, baby. Aren't you
going to tell me what's wrong?

01:07:12.158 --> 01:07:14.926
Ron, I would
really like it

01:07:14.927 --> 01:07:16.896
if you would just
leave me alone.

01:07:16.897 --> 01:07:18.797
- <i>No, come on--</i>
- Please.

01:07:18.798 --> 01:07:21.099
- <i>Don't be like that.</i>
- Please can you just do that for me?

01:07:36.282 --> 01:07:38.250
Okay, all right.

01:07:43.256 --> 01:07:45.924
Well, I love you
very much,

01:07:45.925 --> 01:07:47.626
more than anything.

01:08:04.510 --> 01:08:06.445
That was fucking weird.

01:08:10.750 --> 01:08:13.185
<i>Leonard,</i>
<i>I'm sorry.</i>

01:08:15.955 --> 01:08:18.657
All right, I'll--
I'll call you--

01:08:18.658 --> 01:08:20.892
No no no no, Leonard,
please don't go.

01:08:20.893 --> 01:08:22.795
Please.

01:08:22.796 --> 01:08:24.796
Leonard, could you--

01:08:24.796 --> 01:08:27.131
Will you do me
a favor, please?

01:08:27.133 --> 01:08:29.134
Yeah.

01:08:31.203 --> 01:08:34.171
Could you write something
on my arm with your finger

01:08:34.173 --> 01:08:35.890
while I fall asleep?

01:08:35.892 --> 01:08:39.278
<i>My grandma used to do it</i>
<i>when I was little.</i>

01:09:00.250 --> 01:09:02.216
<i>Mmm.</i>

01:10:12.671 --> 01:10:15.591
<i>...So funny.</i>
<i>Oh, you know what?</i>

01:10:15.592 --> 01:10:19.010
<i>My parents finally got the
pictures back from the bar mitzvah.</i>

01:10:19.011 --> 01:10:22.848
Oh, they-- they like the
dancing shots in the ballroom?

01:10:22.849 --> 01:10:24.816
They love them.

01:10:24.817 --> 01:10:27.102
- Good.
- Thank you, dear.

01:10:27.103 --> 01:10:29.437
You're very welcome.

01:10:29.438 --> 01:10:33.609
Um, I got
something for you.

01:10:35.211 --> 01:10:37.329
- A gift?
- Yeah.

01:10:37.330 --> 01:10:39.147
It's-- you know,
it's winter out, it's cold,

01:10:39.148 --> 01:10:41.683
and I noticed that
you don't wear any gloves.

01:10:41.684 --> 01:10:43.017
Oh, these are nice.

01:10:43.018 --> 01:10:44.603
- Yeah?
- Yeah.

01:10:44.604 --> 01:10:46.104
You like 'em?

01:10:46.105 --> 01:10:47.772
Yeah, it's got
the stitching.

01:10:47.773 --> 01:10:49.474
I've never seen
anything like this.

01:10:49.475 --> 01:10:50.976
- <i>Cool.</i>
- Little silver thing.

01:10:50.977 --> 01:10:52.761
Good.

01:10:56.799 --> 01:10:58.867
That was very sweet
of you. Thanks.

01:10:58.868 --> 01:11:00.735
No big deal.

01:11:07.009 --> 01:11:08.643
What's wrong?
You okay?

01:11:08.644 --> 01:11:09.745
Yeah.

01:11:09.746 --> 01:11:12.180
Yeah, I'm just thinking
about a friend of mine.

01:11:12.181 --> 01:11:14.883
She's kind of going through
some tough stuff, so...

01:11:17.237 --> 01:11:18.870
I don't want you and I
talkin' about it--

01:11:18.871 --> 01:11:20.472
No no,
it's okay.

01:11:24.110 --> 01:11:26.578
I love your hands.

01:11:26.579 --> 01:11:29.381
They're so gentle.

01:11:36.289 --> 01:11:38.724
<i>I hate these</i>
<i>fucking scars.</i>

01:11:41.177 --> 01:11:44.129
Leonard, I, um...

01:11:44.130 --> 01:11:47.649
I want to take care
of you.

01:11:47.650 --> 01:11:49.818
I feel like I
understand you.

01:11:49.819 --> 01:11:51.536
You're different.

01:11:51.537 --> 01:11:54.322
You don't pretend to be
something you're not.

01:11:55.541 --> 01:11:57.876
So you don't have to
worry about anything.

01:11:57.877 --> 01:11:59.878
You don't have to
be embarrassed.

01:11:59.879 --> 01:12:02.347
Thank you.

01:12:02.348 --> 01:12:05.066
You know, I got
a lot of stuff

01:12:05.067 --> 01:12:08.120
going on
right now that's...

01:12:10.707 --> 01:12:12.791
I don't even know what
it's like to just

01:12:12.792 --> 01:12:14.876
be myself right now.

01:12:14.877 --> 01:12:16.944
No, I-- I understand.

01:12:22.201 --> 01:12:24.236
Are you in a hurry
somewhere or what?

01:12:24.237 --> 01:12:25.937
No, I just wanted to
pay the check

01:12:25.938 --> 01:12:27.539
so we could
get out of here.

01:12:27.540 --> 01:12:29.141
Okay.

01:12:29.142 --> 01:12:31.643
Oh, fuck.

01:12:31.644 --> 01:12:34.646
Probably my father calling:
"How's the date?"

01:12:36.482 --> 01:12:39.551
Uh, I gotta take this.
Yeah, it's my friend.

01:12:39.552 --> 01:12:41.553
- Oh, okay.
- I'll be right back.

01:12:41.554 --> 01:12:43.554
Sorry.
We'll go in a minute.

01:12:48.360 --> 01:12:50.161
- Michelle?
